flowchart TD
    Start([START: User wants to create a goal]) --> Auth{Is user authenticated?}
    Auth -->|NO| ShowLogin[Show login/error message]
    ShowLogin --> End1([END])
    Auth -->|YES| SelectType[User selects goal type]
    
    SelectType --> Type{Goal Type?}
    Type -->|QUANTITATIVE| QtyForm[Enter: title, description, category, priority<br/>Enter: startValue, targetValue, currentValue, unit<br/>Set: allowDecimals yes/no<br/>Optional: minValue, maxValue, startDate, deadline]
    Type -->|QUALITATIVE| QualForm[Enter: title, description, category, priority<br/>Set: qualitativeStatus default: not_started<br/>Optional: improvementCriteria, targetRating, startDate, deadline]
    Type -->|BINARY| BinForm[Enter: title, description, category, priority<br/>Optional: targetCount, items array<br/>Set: allowPartialCompletion yes/no<br/>Optional: startDate, deadline]
    Type -->|MILESTONE| MilForm[Enter: title, description, category, priority<br/>Add at least one milestone<br/>For each: title, order, optional description, dueDate, dependencies<br/>Validate no circular dependencies<br/>Set: allowMilestoneReordering, requireSequentialCompletion<br/>Optional: startDate, deadline]
    Type -->|RECURRING| RecForm[Enter: title, description, category, priority<br/>Configure recurrence:<br/>frequency: daily/weekly/monthly/yearly<br/>interval: positive integer<br/>If weekly: daysOfWeek array<br/>If monthly: dayOfMonth optional<br/>If yearly: dayOfYear optional<br/>Optional: endDate, startDate, deadline]
    Type -->|HABIT| HabForm[Enter: title, description, category, priority<br/>Set: targetFrequency daily/every_other_day/weekly/custom<br/>If custom: set customFrequency<br/>Optional: startDate, deadline]
    
    QtyForm --> Validate
    QualForm --> Validate
    BinForm --> Validate
    MilForm --> Validate
    RecForm --> Validate
    HabForm --> Validate
    
    Validate[Validate all required fields] --> Valid{Validation passes?}
    Valid -->|NO| ShowErrors[Show errors]
    ShowErrors --> UserFixes[User fixes]
    UserFixes --> Validate
    Valid -->|YES| Submit[Submit to API]
    
    Submit --> APIResult{API result?}
    APIResult -->|Error| ShowError[Show error message]
    ShowError --> Retry{User retry or cancel?}
    Retry -->|Retry| Submit
    Retry -->|Cancel| End2([END])
    APIResult -->|Success| ShowSuccess[Show success message]
    ShowSuccess --> Navigate[Navigate to goal detail]
    Navigate --> End3([END: Goal created successfully])

    style Start fill:#e1f5ff
    style End1 fill:#ffcdd2
    style End2 fill:#ffcdd2
    style End3 fill:#c8e6c9
    style Auth fill:#fff9c4
    style Type fill:#fff9c4
    style Valid fill:#fff9c4
    style APIResult fill:#fff9c4
    style Retry fill:#fff9c4

